<h1>{{ title }}</h1>

<h2>Tagging taxonomy</h2>

- Primary genre: Fiction, Nonfiction, Magazine.
- Genre subtypes: Science Fiction, Fantasy, Historical Fiction, Gothic Fiction, Literary Fiction, Humor, Memoir.
- Topics: Design, Typography, Information Architecture, UX Research, Accessibility, Product Management, Leadership, Communication, DevOps, Game Development, Cybersecurity, Urbanism, Community, Culture, Science, Space, Breathwork.
- Audience/age: Young Adult, Middle Grade, Children’s.
- Place: New York City, New Orleans, Barcelona.
- Format/meta: Audiobook, Series, Book Club, Magazine, Zine.

{% set allBooks = books | mergeBookLists %}
{% set tagObjs = allBooks | allTagsSorted %}

<section class="tag-index">
  <p>Total books: {{ allBooks | length }}</p>
  <ul>
    {% for t in tagObjs %}
      {% set titles = allBooks | titlesForTag(t.tag) %}
      <li>
        <strong>{{ t.tag | title }} — {{ t.count }}:</strong>
        {{ titles | join(', ') }}
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
</section>